includedAssets.title: Season 1
includedAssets.synopsis: Michael Sheen and Lizzy Caplan star in this stylish and provocative US drama series about the real-life pioneers of the science of human sexuality. Dr William Masters, Washington University's foremost obstetrician and gynaecologist, runs a successful medical practice by day. But by night, he conducts a groundbreaking secret study, and when uninhibited former nightclub singer Virginia Johnson joins the hospital staff, she clicks with the awkward Masters and quickly proves herself to be an asset to his work. Together, their research sparks the sexual revolution and changes their lives forever.
